{"tid":1070821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科大又嬴(沉默的代價)肥雞餐裁110人　資源疑轉移廣州","createTime":"2019-03-21T02:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T07:50:30.000Z","uid":28433,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"755b6dc9682363a0c51ecb855eff904d33090392","tid":1070821,"uid":28433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T02:47:26.000Z","msg":"科大為減省薪酬開支，去年底推出俗稱「肥雞餐」的自願離職方案，向大約300名年資逾廿年的非教學人員開刀。不過直至今年1月15日申請截止，僅約110人自願離職。本報接獲投訴，指不少員工害怕因拒食「肥雞餐」而被針對，無奈下決定自願離職。另有科大消息人士指，校內盛傳部份透過「肥雞餐」離職的員工，將重新獲科大正在籌備的廣州分校前期辦公室聘請，質疑校方千方百計削減大學本部開支，或為了預留相關資源至內地分校。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190320/20637172?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_mweb&amp;itm_content=internal_link_1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190320%2F20637172%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_mweb%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_1&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV4leFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=b3392c6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190320%2F20637172%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_mweb%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_1&h=140a0498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190320/20637172?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_mweb&amp;itm_content=internal_link_1</a><br />\n<br />\n香港科技大學今年起改革全體約1,800名非教學人員的薪酬架構，將他們一半加薪比重改為按表現派發。據悉，校方一直聲稱若表現良好，加薪幅度將優於舊制。但消息人士向《蘋果》稱，科大管理層下令，將可按表現加薪的員工比例限制在三成以內，更向相關部門主管施壓：「如果你唔識做appraisal（評核），我會懷疑你（主管）能力有冇問題」。<br />\n記者：周婷　羅智堅<br />\n<br />\n據悉，科大今年初起要求非教學人員轉制，本月底（3月31日）前須簽署轉制信件，受影響員工包括物業設施管理處人員、人力資源部職員等。科大消息人士稱，目前相關部門「氣氛好差」，主管不斷施壓，「潛台詞就係『你唔簽（轉制文件）就冇運行』」。科大表面上容許職員自行選擇轉制，但指明如果不轉，一旦將來職位有變，不論升職或降職，屆時亦會被轉制。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190320/20637170?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_mweb&amp;itm_content=internal_link_1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190320%2F20637170%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_mweb%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_1&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV4leFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=eaab402a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190320%2F20637170%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_mweb%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_1&h=721542d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190320/20637170?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_mweb&amp;itm_content=internal_link_1</a><br />\n<br />\n班垃圾學者真係自食其果, 之前廢極都有陳雲 戴耀廷出下聲 仲有陳文敏 林慧思 果d . 果時又屌人地搞事 宜家自食其果未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起初他們（德國納粹黨）追殺共產主義者，<br />\n 因為我不是共產主義者，我不說話；<br />\n 接著他們追殺猶太人，<br />\n 因為我不是猶太人，我不說話；<br />\n 後來他們追殺工會成員，<br />\n 因為我不是工會成員，我繼續不說話；<br />\n 此後他們追殺天主教徒，<br />\n 因為我不是天主教徒，我還是不說話；<br />\n 最後，他們奔向我來，<br />\n 再也沒有人站起來為我說話了。"},{"pid":"cf745cdd51acc3dba34b663b945b45bd33c914c5","tid":1070821,"uid":28433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T02:49:49.000Z","msg":"換血成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7df202b9939ca115de7695438bf10505cb08fa2","tid":1070821,"uid":43575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T02:52:54.000Z","msg":"裁非教學職員呀，唔影響到科大學者掛，關沉默的代價咩事？"},{"pid":"26165f96c0b903582904a52384a04ad36cb323fc","tid":1070821,"uid":28433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f7df202b9939ca115de7695438bf10505cb08fa2","tid":1070821,"uid":43575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTim